# OrigenLab marketing page rules

Apply these rules when editing public-facing pages or shared UI sections.

## Primary objective

Every page should help a potential client do one or more of these:
- understand what OrigenLab offers
- find the right product category
- feel trust in the business
- request a quotation
- contact OrigenLab quickly

## Messaging priorities

Prioritize:
1. clarity of offer
2. target customer relevance
3. easy contact
4. professional credibility
5. simple navigation

## Copy style

Write Spanish copy that is:
- direct
- sober
- commercial but not exaggerated
- easy to scan
- suitable for B2B audiences in Chile

Avoid:
- empty slogans
- exaggerated claims
- long walls of text
- vague statements like "soluciones innovadoras de clase mundial" unless supported

Prefer:
- short section intros
- concrete category labels
- trust-building service language
- visible contact actions

## Approved business framing

Safe statements include ideas like:
- venta de equipos para laboratorio
- atención a clientes en todo Chile
- apoyo en selección de equipos según necesidad
- soporte, asesoría, instalación y puesta en marcha en equipos más complejos
- contacto para cotización y consultas

Unsafe statements unless confirmed:
- representantes oficiales de marcas específicas
- servicio técnico certificado
- stock inmediato
- despacho garantizado en cierto plazo
- cobertura técnica nacional presencial
- cumplimiento normativo específico

## CTA patterns

Prefer one clear CTA per section. Examples:
- Solicitar cotización
- Hablar por WhatsApp
- Contactar a OrigenLab
- Ver categorías
- Solicitar información

## Layout/content guidance

A good page structure is usually:
- clear hero
- brief explanation of offer
- category or service blocks
- trust/support section
- contact CTA
- footer with direct contact details

## SEO/content guidance

When improving pages:
- use a single clear H1
- use descriptive H2s
- mention audience and category terms naturally
- keep title/description aligned with real content
- avoid keyword stuffing

## Contact defaults

If a contact block is needed and no explicit data source exists, use:
- contacto@origenlab.cl
- +56 9 6256 7816
- WhatsApp same number
- **Valdivia, Chile** (same as `contact.locationPublic` — no street on public pages unless product owner explicitly requires it)
